            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Do you have some sort of a secret?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hm, maybe it's my strictly regulated lifestyle?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "What are you talking about?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Sophie. Corneria was just asking me about how to grow taller."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Taller?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Yes, I thought Monika would know how..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Oh yeah, Monika's pretty tall after all. I'm kind of jealous."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "...Really?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. You're really stylish, and you look picture perfect no matter what you're doing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I wouldn't go THAT far..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Also, I think your smaller stature is cute. I feel jealous about that sometimes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x26,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Wait, really?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I don't think so..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I suppose we all just want things that we don't have."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x28,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I guess so..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, I'll be going now."
